FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773288217
OL,3,CTim Davie says trust in institutions
OL,4,Clike BBC in 'full on crisis'
OL,6,FMr Davie's appearance on the podcast
OL,7,Fcomes as the BBC has come under fire
OL,8,Fmore recently, after a racial slur was
OL,9,Fbroadcast during its coverage of the
OL,10,FBafta film awards last month.
OL,12,FMr Davie has previously described the
OL,13,Fincident as a "genuine mistake" and
OL,14,Fsaid the BBC takes "full
OL,15,Fresponsibility for our error".
OL,17,FThe full episode of The Rest Is
OL,18,FEntertainment is available to be
OL,19,Flistened to now.
OL,26,@uD@OOUuD@_O]vD@TOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
